OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some patchy rain. Then this
OL,7,Fafternoon will be largely dry with
OL,8,Fsome occasional brightness breaking
OL,9,Fthrough the cloud. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,12,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,13,Fcloudy with some rain spreading to
OL,14,Fwest counties, remaining dry across
OL,15,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
