OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,6,Fspreading eastwards across all parts
OL,7,Fin the morning. Drier weather
OL,8,Ffollowing on behind during the
OL,9,Fafternoon, reaching the east coast by
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cold
OL,13,Fstart with some frost on Friday, then
OL,14,Fa dry and sunny day, Dry and bright on
OL,15,FSaturday, clouding over later. Cloudy
OL,16,Fwith a chance of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
